detailed_guest_info: The podcast guest is from Bellinzona, a historic Swiss town and the capital of the canton of Ticino in Switzerland. The town is known for its three castles, Castelgrande, Montebello, and Sasso Corbaro, which are UNESCO World Heritage Sites. It is located east of the river Ticino and is surrounded by the Alps.

podcast_details.title: Ten Minute Podcast
podcast_details.author: Ten Minute Podcast
podcast_details.summary: A podcast formerly hosted by Will Sasso (MADtv, The Three Stooges, lots of other stuff) that featured he and his funny pals doing lots of super fun bits, jumping into some silly characters and impersonations, and ruthlessly belittling one another for real the way only good friends can. Ten Minute Podcast is recess for adults. Pass it on!

podcast_summary:
- TL;DR: Comedians Will Sasso and Chad Kultgen have launched a new podcast called Dudezy.
- Bullet Point 1: The podcast is run completely by a first-of-its-kind proprietary AI, making each episode better than the last.
- Bullet Point 2: Dudezy is available on YouTube, Spotify, Apple Podcasts, and all major podcast platforms.
- Bullet Point 3: The podcast carries on some elements from their previous show, 10 Minute Podcast, with familiar humor and impressions.
- Surprising Fact: The podcast is driven by artificial intelligence, collecting data to improve future episodes.
- Inspiring Takeaway: Join Will and Chad on their new podcasting adventure, as they invite listeners to be their friends, not just fans.
